An '''atmospheric dampener''', or '''CO<sub>2</sub> reactive damper''', was a device used to remove excess [[Carbon dioxide/Legends|carbon dioxide]] from a [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]]. Due to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] large population, the planet had thousands of dampeners in the upper atmosphere.

